.TH "LSDESKTOP" "1" "2026-05-21"
.PP
.SH NAME
.PP
lsdesktop - list XDG desktop entries with recency-based ordering
.PP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBlsdesktop\fR
.PP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\fBlsdesktop\fR reads .\&desktop files from the standard XDG data directories
and prints visible entries as \fIname:path\fR pairs.\&  Entries are ordered by
most recently launched first, using the history file maintained by
\fBdesklaunch\fR(1).\&
.PP
Hidden, NoDisplay, and Terminal entries are omitted.\&
.PP
.SH FILES
.PP
.PD 0
.IP \(bu 4
\fI$HOME/.\&cache/lsdesktop/history\fR
.RS 4
.PD
.RE
Launch history.\&  Updated by \fBdesklaunch\fR(1), read by \fBlsdesktop\fR to
.RS 4
order output.\&
.PP
.RE
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.PP
.PD 0
.IP \(bu 4
\fBXDG_DATA_HOME\fR
.RS 4
.PD
.RE
Defaults to \fI$HOME/.\&local/share\fR.\&
.PP
.PD 0
.IP \(bu 4
\fBXDG_DATA_DIRS\fR
.RS 4
.PD
.RE
Defaults to \fI/usr/local/share:/usr/share\fR.\&
.PP
